sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant UI as Bayand UI
  participant BE as Rust Backend
  participant AUTH as auth row
  participant DB as bayand.db
  participant BK as backups

  U->>UI: Enter password
  UI->>BE: unlock_tracker(password)
  BE->>AUTH: Load password salt and wrapped key
  AUTH-->>BE: Stored auth metadata
  BE->>BE: Argon2 derive wrapping key
  BE->>BE: AES-256-GCM unwrap master key
  BE->>DB: Open encrypted tracker
  BE->>BK: backup_and_rotate()
  BE->>BE: Cache unlocked session state
  BE-->>UI: authState = unlocked

  Note over BE,UI: lock_tracker clears in-memory secrets and returns the app to locked state
